{"tid":1797684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（即刻答，唔準諗）其實而家既五大訴求係咩？","createTime":"2019-12-25T15:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:47:16.000Z","uid":4050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50448017507f5517f49ba54ae6b76ba50a87fd7f","tid":1797684,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"6，7月嗰陣，好明確的，淺黃淺藍都會知五大訴求係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 撒回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 釋放義士<br />\n3. 撒回暴動定性<br />\n4. 獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 雙普選<br />\n<br />\n而家係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 解散警隊<br />\n2. 釋放義士<br />\n3. 撒回暴動定性<br />\n4. 獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 雙普選<br />\n<br />\n我問過身邊淺黃既朋友，大家都好似有唔同既版本，有人話係特赦義士唔係釋放義士，又有人話唔係解散警隊，而係追究警隊濫權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地係咪要再重申下咩係五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0c35a30bfbe3da81b2130be8a51ca691ac2357","tid":1797684,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c457ae731a5de2164c99d4813da76c5a75d912","tid":1797684,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb42633809e956b69846a17616fb1dd6283b241","tid":1797684,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857e406fb6acc50faad60d7de4d5fe2dd7770e3a","tid":1797684,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e0b84af6cb81cf6a91a41ddc822d59d32e6bdfd7","tid":1797684,"uid":96431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460c94638008f3ca7d48766758a99b9df23d0553","tid":1797684,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有自由意志的香港人唔會唔知，但要拉攏的淺黃港豬就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5d45f527cfd147f174f5ca42612e62b4f556681a","tid":1797684,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"1. 全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤銷抗爭者控罪<br />\n3. 撤回暴動定性<br />\n4. 獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 真雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">缺一不可</span></strong></span>"}]}